column5: I hope he makes it. How long has he been on ECMO?

They may be operating as agents for the CCP. If so, they are acting as mouthpieces for the party. There are rings of these agents in the US, spying on and intimidating Chinese-Americans. Those who are in academia or attend religious gatherings are especially targeted.

 The Chinese government is anything but honest. Look at the numbers of their own citizens who have been locked up and brutally murdered. Thousands have disappeared. Never to be seen again. Some prisoners have even had their organs harvested involuntarily. The government has attempted to erase the history of Tiananmen Square. . They deny having internment camps for dissidents. . . Whistleblower doctors have gone missing . . Yet we are to trust these authoritarians on their covid numbers?
He needs to wear a mask when socializing
I hope you are still with us
I wonder if he sits down every day and thinks, "Hmmm .. How can I make this crisis even worse?"

I can only imagine what you're going through. This pandemic has caused a great deal of stress on everyone, but medical professionals are experiencing 100x the amount of stress. Secondary trauma is real now more than ever.
I sincerely hope today will be better for you, and that there are positive people you can surround yourself with .
